_us_text','We love to do what we do every day. Founded in 2008, <strong>ITU Management Services (ISO 9001: 2015)</strong> offers you a wide range of healthcare solutions and services including <em>i)</em> One-Stop-Shop Solution for TPA Cashless Management <em>ii)</em> OPD/IPD Patient Engagement Solution and <em>iii)</em> Medical Tourism Solution & Services.\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Being a pioneer in the field of healthcare with over 15 years of domain expertise, our team has succeeded in reaching up to our clients’ expectations till date and still working hard to excel even further by following today’s best practices.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our team consists of more than 150+ dedicated professionals with varied backgrounds and diverse experiences. Although we work in a very complicated commercial landscape with multiple stakeholders involved in the sphere, we nurture all our stakeholders very delicately in order to continue with our seamless operations. Our ultimate goal is to achieve operational efficiency, increased revenue flow and enhance the brand value of our end clients (multi-specialty hospitals, super-specialty hospitals) along with maintaining trust and good-will in our field of work.</p>'),(337,10,'_about_us_text','field_5e7cc7456e70c'),(338,10,'about_us_image','178'),(339,10,'_about_us_image','field_5e7cc76b6e70d'),(340,10,'our_mission_field','<div class=\"about-icon\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-88 size-full\" src=\"https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/mission.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></div>\r\n<h2>OUR MISSION</h2>\r\nIn a nutshell, we work not only to help reputed hospitals and corporate organizations operate better but also enable common individuals to live a completely hassle-free life. We aspire to transform the healthcare industry through our fit-for purpose solutions and services, thereby creating a brighter tomorrow for the patients across our nation.'),(341,10,'_our_mission_field','field_5e7cc7fa6e70e'),(342,10,'our_vision_field','<div class=\"about-icon\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-90 size-full\" src=\"https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/vision.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></div>\r\n<h2>OUR VISION</h2>\r\nWe envision to become the ‘Brand Ambassador’ of healthcare solutions and the best-in-class service provider, offering services which cater to all industry stakeholders starting from hospitals, doctors, nurses to corporate, patients and medical travelers, so that the entire healthcare ecosystem can benefit through our value offerings.'),(343,10,'_our_vision_field','field_5e7cc8136e70f'),(344,10,'how_we_work_field',''),(345,10,'_how_we_work_field','field_5e7cc8266e710'),(346,10,'our_beliefs_field',''),(347,10,'_our_beliefs_field','field_5e7cc8336e711'),(348,10,'domain_expertise_field','<div class=\"reputation-icon-wrapper\">[icon name=\"ambulance\" class=\"\" unprefixed_class=\"\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"about-counter-wrapper\"><span class=\"counter01\">20</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"counter-title\">\r\n<h3>years of domain expertise</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"divider divider01\"></div>\r\n<!--\r\n<div class=\"counter-exeption\">Being a pioneer in the field of healthcare with over 15 years of domain expertise, our team works closely with Insurance companies and Third Party Administrators (TPAs) to provide end-to-end management services to both hospitals and patients, starting from processing personal insurance documents to recovery of health insurance claims by following a strategic workflow.</div>\r\n-->'),(349,10,'_domain_expertise_field','field_5e7ccad76e712'),(350,10,'employees_field','<div class=\"reputation-icon-wrapper\">[icon name=\"users\" class=\"\" unprefixed_class=\"\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"about-counter-wrapper\"><span class=\"counter02\">100</span>+</div>\r\n<div class=\"counter-title\">\r\n<h3>Qualified Employees</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"divider divider01\"></div>\r\n<!--\r\n<div class=\"co