g hard to excel even further by following today’s best practices.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our team consists of more than 150+ dedicated professionals with varied backgrounds and diverse experiences. Although we work in a very complicated commercial landscape with multiple stakeholders involved in the sphere, we nurture all our stakeholders very delicately in order to continue with our seamless operations. Our ultimate goal is to achieve operational efficiency, increased revenue flow and enhance the brand value of our end clients (multi-specialty hospitals, super-specialty hospitals) along with maintaining trust and good-will in our field of work.</p>'),(1819,365,'_about_us_text','field_5e7cc7456e70c'),(1820,365,'about_us_image','178'),(1821,365,'_about_us_image','field_5e7cc76b6e70d'),(1822,365,'our_mission_field','<div class=\"about-icon\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-88 size-full\" src=\"http://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/mission.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></div>\r\n<h2>OUR MISSION</h2>\r\nIn a nutshell, we work not only to help reputed hospitals and corporate organizations operate better but also enable common individuals to live a completely hassle-free life. We aspire to transform the healthcare industry through our fit-for purpose solutions and services, thereby creating a brighter tomorrow for the patients across our nation.'),(1823,365,'_our_mission_field','field_5e7cc7fa6e70e'),(1824,365,'our_vision_field','<div class=\"about-icon\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-90 size-full\" src=\"http://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/vision.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></div>\r\n<h2>OUR VISION</h2>\r\nWe envision to become the ‘Brand Ambassador’ of healthcare solutions and the best-in-class service provider, offering services which cater to all industry stakeholders starting from hospitals, doctors, nurses to corporate, patients and medical travelers, so that the entire healthcare ecosystem can benefit through our value offerings.'),(1825,365,'_our_vision_field','field_5e7cc8136e70f'),(1826,365,'how_we_work_field','<div class=\"about-icon\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-91 size-full\" src=\"http://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/workflow.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></div>\r\n<h2>HOW WE WORK</h2>\r\nTo provide hassle free services to each insured patient/individual, we offer our integrated cashless and claim re-imbursement service to esteemed hospitals and corporate organizations. Our operation not only entails processing claims on behalf of patients but also entails following up with enhancements from insurance companies later, along with a fast recovery process of insurance claims for our clients (hospitals). We trust our stakeholders and maintain a very sound and transparent working relationship with each and every individual within the industry. Our strong and active network in the healthcare sector, along with our domain expertise, surely gives us a competitive edge over others in the commercial sphere.'),(1827,365,'_how_we_work_field','field_5e7cc8266e710'),(1828,365,'our_beliefs_field','<div class=\"about-icon\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-92 size-full\" src=\"http://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/biliefs.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></div>\r\n<h2>OUR BELIEFS</h2>\r\nWe believe in transparency, trust, commitment and teamwork. We bring motivated people at work to address the needs of super-specialty hospitals, multi-specialty hospitals, corporate organizations and common individuals. Our goal is all about ensuring better insurance management system for our clients at the clients\' sites itself, i.e. within the hospital premises by introducing a separate Health Insurance (TPA) Helpdesk support exclusively for corporate and non-corporate patients, both during the time of admission and discharge. This not only helps us interacting directly with patients but also providing them or their family the customized su