formance based incentives are given to those who establish themselves as top performers by driving results.'),(1904,326,'_perk_text_2','field_5ead96b18716d'),(1905,326,'perk_icon_3','403'),(1906,326,'_perk_icon_3','field_5ead96b88716e'),(1907,326,'perk_text_3','<h1>Industry Recognition</h1>\r\nITU Management Services is the only company in this line of work which is ISO 9001:2015 certified and has high quality of systems, processes and infrastructure for employees. Our team members get a lot of opportunities to interact with various industry leaders in the healthcare sector and also participate in various healthcare events.'),(1908,326,'_perk_text_3','field_5ead96bf8716f'),(1909,326,'perk_icon_4','405'),(1910,326,'_perk_icon_4','field_5ead96c887170'),(1911,326,'perk_text_4','<h1>Health Benefits</h1>\r\nWe offer consistent health benefits to our employees including health insurance policies and related support. ITUMS, being in the healthcare space, make special arrangement for logistics and bed-side support for employees and their family members, during the time of crisis and emergency.'),(1912,326,'_perk_text_4','field_5ead96cc87171'),(1913,326,'perk_icon_5','407'),(1914,326,'_perk_icon_5','field_5ead96d187172'),(1915,326,'perk_text_5','<h1>In Office Celebrations &amp; Events</h1>\r\nOur team follows a clan culture and our team members are jovial and vibrant at work. They celebrate occasions like foundation day, birthdays, festive bonus-day, etc. Team ITU Management Services has a corporate tie-up with JW Marriott Hotels where team members go to throw success parties, especially after big achievements.'),(1916,326,'_perk_text_5','field_5ead96d587173'),(1917,326,'perk_icon_6','408'),(1918,326,'_perk_icon_6','field_5ead96da87174'),(1919,326,'perk_text_6','<h1>Creative Open Workspaces</h1>\r\nWe encourage team members to come up with creative ideas at work. We promote fresh opinions at our workplace. We also follow a very open work culture where everyone is given equal