rder to continue with our seamless operations. Our ultimate goal is to achieve operational efficiency, increased revenue flow and enhance the brand value of our end clients (multi-specialty hospitals, super-specialty hospitals) along with maintaining trust and good-will in our field of work.</p>'),(2619,452,'_about_us_text','field_5e7cc7456e70c'),(2620,452,'about_us_image','178'),(2621,452,'_about_us_image','field_5e7cc76b6e70d'),(2622,452,'our_mission_field','<div class=\"about-icon\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-88 size-full\" src=\"http://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/mission.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></div>\r\n<h2>OUR MISSION</h2>\r\nIn a nutshell, we work not only to help reputed hospitals and corporate organizations operate better but also enable common individuals to live a completely hassle-free life. We aspire to transform the healthcare industry through our fit-for purpose solutions and services, thereby creating a brighter tomorrow for the patients across our nation.'),(2623,452,'_our_mission_field','field_5e7cc7fa6e70e'),(2624,452,'our_vision_field','<div class=\"about-icon\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-90 size-full\" src=\"http://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/vision.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></div>\r\n<h2>OUR VISION</h2>\r\nWe envision to become the ‘Brand Ambassador’ of healthcare solutions and the best-in-class service provider, offering services which cater to all industry stakeholders starting from hospitals, doctors, nurses to corporate, patients and medical travelers, so that the entire healthcare ecosystem can benefit through our value offerings.'),(2625,452,'_our_vision_field','field_5e7cc8136e70f'),(2626,452,'how_we_work_field','<div class=\"about-icon\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-91 size-full\" src=\"http://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/workflow.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></div>\r\n<h2>HOW WE WORK</h2>\r\nTo provide hassle free services to each insured 