mplete assistance in training</li>\r\n 	<li>Obtain marketing materials along with guidance in advertising and promotion</li>\r\n 	<li>Assistance on video call on the final day of your customer presentation</li>\r\n 	<li>Empanelment Advisory Support &amp; Consulting</li>\r\n 	<li>Assistance on Contract Agreements and Negotiations with your customers</li>\r\n 	<li>Assistance on Sales/Revenue Forecast and Growth Plan</li>\r\n 	<li>Last but not the least - our TOTAL commitment to you</li>\r\n</ul>'),(3245,538,'about_us_text','Our story began in 2008 when our Founder - <strong>Mr. Jayanta Bhowmick</strong>, started providing TPA Cashless Management Services in Kolkata, with a team of 3 people. Today, we are privileged to associate ourselves with reputed clients, global brands and millions of patients every day through our exceptional services and quality of work. Today, we are proud to be a big family with more than 150 members in our team.\r\n\r\nITU is the name of our Founder’s Mother. And our Logo is also inspired by a tree – featuring with roots &amp; leafs, which indicates our strength and unity.\r\n\r\nBeing a pioneer in the field of healthcare with over 15+ years of domain expertise, <strong>ITU Management Services (ISO 9001:2015)</strong> offers a wide range of healthcare solutions and services including - i) TPA Cashless Management Solution for Hospitals, ii) Empanelment Management Solution for Hospitals, iii) OPD/IPD Patient Engagement Solution for Hospitals, iv) Medical Tourism Solution for Hospitals &amp; Patients, v) TPA Desk Management Services for Hospitals, vi) TPA Reimbursement Management Services for Patients, vii) Floor Operations &amp; Marketing Services for Hospitals and viii) Patient Logistics for Medical Tourists and Ambulance Service for Patients'),(3246,538,'_about_us_text','field_5e7cc7456e70c'),(3247,538,'about_us_image','178'),(3248,538,'_about_us_image','field_5e7cc76b6e70d'),(3249,538,'our_mission_field','<div class=\"about-icon\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-88 size-full\" src=\"https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/mission.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></div>\r\n<h2>OUR MISSION</h2>\r\nIn a nutshell, we work not only to help reputed hospitals and corporate organizations operate better but also enable common individuals to live a completely hassle-free life. We aspire to transform the healthcare industry through our fit-for purpose solutions and services, thereby creating a brighter tomorrow for the patients across our nation.'),(3250,538,'_our_mission_field','field_5e7cc7fa6e70e'),(3251,538,'our_vision_field','<div class=\"about-icon\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-90 size-full\" src=\"https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/vision.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></div>\r\n<h2>OUR VISION</h2>\r\nWe envision to become the ‘Brand Ambassador’ of healthcare solutions and the best-in-class service provider, offering services which cater to all industry stakeholders starting from hospitals, doctors, nurses to corporate, patients and medical travelers, so that the entire healthcare ecosystem can benefit through our value offerings.'),(3252,538,'_our_vision_field','field_5e7cc8136e70f'),(3253,538,'how_we_work_field','<div class=\"about-icon\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-91 size-full\" src=\"https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/workflow.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></div>\r\n<h2>HOW WE WORK</h2>\r\nTo provide hassle free services to each insured patient/individual, we offer our integrated cashless and claim re-imbursement service to esteemed hospitals and corporate organizations. Our operation not only entails processing claims on behalf of patients but also entails following up with enhancements from insurance companies later, along with a fast recovery process of insurance claims for our clients (hospitals). We trust our stakeholders and maintain a very sound and transparent working relationship with each and every individual within the industry. Our strong and active network in the healthcare sector, along with our domain expertise, surely gives us a competitive edge over others in the commercial sphere.'),(3254,538,'_how_we_work_field','field_5e7cc8266e710'),(3255,538,'our_beliefs_field','<div class=\"about-icon\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-92 size-full\" src=\"https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/biliefs.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></div>\r\n<h2>OUR BELIEFS</h2>\r\nWe believe in transparency, trust, commitment and teamwork. We bring motivated people at work to address the needs of super-specialty hospitals, multi-specialty hospitals, corporate organizations and common individuals. Our goal is all about ensuring better insurance management system for our clients at the clients\' sites itself, i.e. within the hospital premises by introducing a separate Health Insurance (TPA) Helpdesk support exclusively for corporate and non-corporate patients, both during the time of admission and discharge. This not only helps us interacting directly with patients but also providing them or their family the customized support depending on their needs.'),(3256,538,'_our_beliefs_field','field_5e7cc8336e711'),(3257,538,'domain_expertise_field','<div class=\"reputation-icon-wrapper\">[icon name=\"ambulance\" class=\"\" unprefixed_class=\"\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"about-counter-wrapper\"><span class=\"counter01\">20</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"counter-title\">\r\n<h3>years of domain expertise</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"divider divider01\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"counter-exeption\">Being a pioneer in the field of healthcare with over 15 years of domain expertise, our team works closely with Insurance companies and Third Party Administrators (TPAs) to provide end-to-end management services to both hospitals and patients, starting from processing personal insurance documents to recovery of health insurance claims by following a strategic workflow.</div>'),(3258,538,'_domain_expert