 for Hospitals, iv) Medical Tourism Solution for Hospitals &amp; Patients, v) TPA Desk Management Services for Hospitals, vi) TPA Reimbursement Management Services for Patients, vii) Floor Operations &amp; Marketing Services for Hospitals and viii) Patient Logistics for Medical Tourists and Ambulance Service for Patients'),(4543,788,'about_us_text','Our story began in 2008 when our Founder - <strong>Mr. Jayanta Bhowmick</strong>, started providing TPA Cashless Management Services in Kolkata, with a team of 3 people. Today, we are privileged to associate ourselves with reputed clients, global brands and millions of patients every day through our exceptional services and quality of work. Today, we are proud to be a big family with more than 150 members in our team.\r\n\r\nITU is the name of our Founder’s Mother. And our Logo is also inspired by a tree – featuring with roots &amp; leafs, which indicates our strength and unity.\r\n\r\nBeing a pioneer in the field of healthcare with over 15+ years of domain expertise, <strong>ITU Management Services (ISO 9001:2015)</strong> offers a wide range of healthcare solutions and services including - i) TPA Cashless Management Solution for Hospitals, ii) Empanelment Management Solution for Hospitals, iii) OPD/IPD Patient Engagement Solution for Hospitals, iv) Medical Tourism Solution for Hospitals &amp; Patients, v) TPA Desk Management Services for Hospitals, vi) TPA Reimbursement Management Services for Patients, vii) Floor Operations &amp; Marketing Services for Hospitals and viii) Patient Logistics for Medical Tourists and Ambulance Service for Patients'),(4544,788,'_about_us_text','field_5e7cc7456e70c'),(4545,788,'about_us_image','178'),(4546,788,'_about_us_image','field_5e7cc76b6e70d'),(4547,788,'our_mission_field','<div class=\"about-icon\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-88 size-full\" src=\"https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/mission.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></div>\r\n<h2>OUR MISSION</h2>\r\nIn a nutshell, we work not only to help reputed hospitals and corporate organizations operate better but also enable common individuals to live a completely hassle-free life. We aspire to transform the healthcare industry through our fit-for purpose solutions and services, thereby creating a brighter tomorrow for the patients across our nation.'),(4548,788,'_our_mission_field','field_5e7cc7fa6e70e'),(4549,788,'our_vision_field','<div class=\"about-icon\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-90 size-full\" src=\"https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/vision.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></div>\r\n<h2>OUR VISION</h2>\r\nWe envision to become the ‘Brand Ambassador’ of healthcare solutions and the best-in-class service provider, offering services which cater to all industry stakeholders starting from hospitals, doctors, nurses to corporate, patients and medical travelers, so that the entire healthcare ecosystem can benefit through our value offerings.'),(4550,788,'_our_vision_field','field_5e7cc8136e70f'),(4551,788,'how_we_work_field','<div class=\"about-icon\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-91 size-full\" src=\"https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/workflow.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></div>\r\n<!-- <h2>HOW WE WORK</h2>\r\nTo provide hassle free services to each insured patient/individual, we offer our integrated cashless and claim re-imbursement service to esteemed hospitals and corporate organizations. Our operation not only entails processing claims on behalf of patients but also entails following up with enhancements from insurance companies later, along with a fast recovery process of insurance claims for our clients (hospitals). We trust our stakeholders and maintain a very sound and transparent working relationship with each and every individual within the industry. Our strong and active network in the healthcare sector, along with our domain expertise, surely gives us a competitive edge over others in the commercial sp