s about key developments and progress, on a daily basis.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div id=\"service03\">\r\n<div class=\"solution-left\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/tpa-reimbursement-management.png\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"solution-right\">\r\n<h3>TPA Reimbursement management</h3>\r\n<div class=\"service-text\">In order to ensure patient satisfaction, we do offer Reimbursement Solutions after doing a case by case analysis. There are instances where the patients, in spite of being insured, do not get the final approval from TPAs to avail cashless services. In these particular cases, we do all necessary consultations with the patient parties and coordinate with TPAs immediately to get the reimbursements on behalf of the patients, as quickly as possible.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div id=\"service04\">\r\n<div class=\"solution-left\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/hospital-floor-marketing-operations.png\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"solution-right\">\r\n<h3>Hospital Floor Marketing Operations</h3>\r\n<div class=\"service-text\">This service is a part of our OPD/IPD Patient Engagement Solution. Through our services, we make sure we turn to each and every patient on the hospital floor, greet them and offer them help and assistance all throughout their journey within the hospital. Our aim is to engage with each and every patient, help them not only during the stay (related to pharmacy, billing, TPA queries etc.) but also stay connected post visit and operations.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div id=\"service05\">\r\n<div class=\"solution-left\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/patient-logistics-services-medical-tourism.png\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"solution-right\">\r\n<h3>Patient Logistics Services for Medical Tourism</h3>\r\n<div class=\"service-text\">ITUMS have a dedicated Logistics Team not only to arrange for visas, flights and accommodations for medical travelers but also provide all kinds of support related to commuting including airport transfers, hotel pick-up and drop facilities along with commuting to hospitals. In a nutshell, we stay by the medical travelers throughout their medical journey in order to ensure they have a very satisfying and pleasant experience during the entire visit.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div id=\"service06\">\r\n<div class=\"solution-left\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/ambulance-services.png\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"solution-right\">\r\n<h3>Ambulance Services</h3>\r\n<div class=\"service-text\">ITU Management Services provide Ambulance services for patients in cases of emergencies. To avail our service or to book an ambulance, please call us at (033) 4060 2084.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Our Services','','publish','closed','closed','','our-services','','','2020-06-26 10:20:09','2020-06-26 10:20:09','',0,'http://itums.co.in/?page_id=303',0,'page','',0),(302,1,'2020-04-04 03:17:37','2020-04-04 03:17:37','','Solutions','','publish','closed','closed','','solutions','','','2020-07-02 07:05:03','2020-07-02 07:05:03','',0,'http://itums.co.in/?p=302',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(305,1,'2020-06-24 08:43:59','2020-06-24 08:43:59','<div id=\"service01\">\n<div class=\"solution-left\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/hospital-tpa-desk-management.png\" /></div>\n<div class=\"solution-right\">\n<h3>Hospital TPA Desk Management</h3>\n<div class=\"service-text\">Besides our TPA Cashless Digital Web Portal solution, we also provide exclusive manpower support to manage TPA desk operations at hospitals, as needed by our clients. Our team members are extremely well trained and well able to provide all the necessary consultations and support when it comes to dealing with patients, replying to medical/non-medical q