ution-left\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/solution-img-01.png\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"solution-right\">\r\n<h3>TPA Cashless Digital Web Portal Solution</h3>\r\n<div class=\"service-text\">ITU Management Services provide one-stop-shop Mediclaim Cashless Management Solution, starting from processing personal insurance documents to recovery of health insurance claims by following a strategic workflow.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div id=\"solution02\">\r\n<div class=\"solution-left\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/solution-img-02.png\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"solution-right\">\r\n<h3>Empanelment Management Solution</h3>\r\n<div class=\"service-text\">ITU Management Services provide a unique Empanelment Management Solution for hospitals to centralize all Empanelment document processing and operations with Third Party Administrators (TPAs) along with the provision of secured storage of all documents.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div id=\"solution03\">\r\n<div class=\"solution-left\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/solution-img-03.png\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"solution-right\">\r\n<h3>OPD/IPD Patient Engagement Solution</h3>\r\n<div class=\"service-text\">ITU Management Services provide a unique OPD/IPD Patient Engagement Solution for hospitals not only to increase the patient influx but also to create a long-lasting impression on patients for the long term retention and building a trustworthy relationship with them, over the years.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div id=\"solution04\">\r\n<div class=\"solution-left\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/solution-img-04.png\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"solution-right\">\r\n<h3>Medical Tourism Solution</h3>\r\n<div class=\"service-text\">ITU Management Services have the strongest network of reputed hospitals, renowned doctors, along with travel and insurance experts within India which define a very unique value chain for foreign patients and make sure that they feel very comfortable and relaxed throughout their entire medical stay at your hospital.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Our Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','303-revision-v1','','','2020-06-24 04:29:22','2020-06-24 04:29:22','',303,'https://itums.co.in/303-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(469,1,'2020-05-06 13:28:53','2020-05-06 13:28:53','<div id=\"service01\" class=\"service-section\">\r\n<div class=\"service-left\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"http://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/medical-services-image.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"service-right\">\r\n<h4>Hospital TPA Desk Management</h4>\r\n<section class=\"service-text\">\r\nBesides our TPA Cashless Digital Web Portal solution, we also provide exclusive manpower support to manage TPA desk operations at hospitals, as needed by our clients. Our team members are extremely well trained and well able to provide all the necessary consultations and support when it comes to dealing with patients, replying to medical/non-medical queries along with overall document management including billing.\r\n</section></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div id=\"service02\" class=\"service-section\">\r\n<div class=\"service-left\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"http://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/medical-services-image.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"service-right\">\r\n<h4>TPA &amp; Corporate Empanelment management</h4>\r\n<section class=\"service-text\">\r\nOur Team provides exclusive manpower support for hospitals by preparing all documents that are needed to apply for ROHINI ID and empanelment with all TPAs and Corporates. We have a dedicated Empanelment Team and we provide a dedicated Empanelment Manager to each and every client. We track progress offline and also through our web-portal and update our clients about key developments and progress, on a daily basis.\r\n</section></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div id=\"service03\" class=\"service-section\">\r\n<div class=\"service-left\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"http://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/medical-services-image.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"service-right\">\r\n<h4>TPA Reimbursement management</h4>\r\n<section class=\"service-text\">\r\nIn order to ensure patient satisfaction, we do offer Reimbursement Solutions after doing a case by case analysis. There are instances where the patients, in spite of being insured, do not get the final approval from TPAs to avail cashless services. In these particular cases, we do all necessary consultations with the patient parties and coordinate with TPAs immediately to get the reimbursements on behalf of the patients, as quickly as possible.\r\n</section></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div id=\"service04\" class=\"service-section\">\r\n<div class=\"service-left\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"http://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/medical-services-image.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"service-right\">\r\n<h4>Hospital Floor Marketing Operations</h4>\r\n<section class=\"service-text\">\r\nThis service is a part of our OPD/IPD Patient Engagement Solution. Through our services, we make sure we turn to each and every patient on the hospital floor, greet them and offer them help and assistance all throughout their journey within the hospital. Our aim is to engage with each and every patient, help them not only during the stay (related to pharmacy, billing, TPA queries etc.) but also stay connected post visit and operations.\r\n</section></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div id=\"service05\" class=\"service-section\">\r\n<div class=\"service-left\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"http://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/medical-services-image.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"service-right\">\r\n<h4>Patient Logistics Services for Medical Tourism</h4>\r\n<section class=\"service-text\">\r\nITUMS have a dedicated Logistics Team not only to arrange for visas, flights and accommodations for medical travelers but also provide all kinds of support related to commuting including airport transfers, hotel pick-up and drop facilities along with commuting to hospitals. In a nutshell, we stay by the medical travelers throughout their medical journey in order to ensure they have a very satisfying and pleasant experience during the entire visit.\r\n</section></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div id=\"service06\" class=\"service-section\">\r\n<div class=\"service-left\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"http://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/medical-services-image.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"service-right\">\r\n<h4>Ambulance Services</h4>\r\n<section class=\"service-text\">\r\nITU Management Services provide Ambulance services for patients in cases of emergencies. To avail our service or to book to book am ambulance, please call us at +91-98300-13731.\r\n</section></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />','Our Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','303-revision-v1','','','2020-05-06 13:28:53','2020-05-06 13:28:53','',303,'http://itums.co.in/303-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(472,1,'2020-05-06 13:48:13','2020-05-06 13:48:13','ITU Management Services is the pioneer in the field of healthcare industry with domain expertise of more than 15 years. ITUMS has chosen the franchise system of growth to extend our footprint across PAN India.  ITUMS is the fastest growing franchise in West Bengal and also across India. ITUMS is inviting entrepreneurs who wish to join our family and grow with us. Team ITUMS assures all franchise owners guaranteed success and growth path. As we are an asset light model, potential for growth is unlimited while chances of incurring losses are extremely low in our line of service.','Franchise','Our Franchise page','inherit','closed','closed','','193-revision-v1','','','2020-05-06 13:48:13','2020-05-06 1