\nany changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.\r\n\r\nWe will let you know via email and/or a prominent notice on Our Service,\r\nprior to the change becoming effective and update the \"Last updated\" date\r\nat the top of this Privacy Policy.\r\n\r\nYou are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.\r\nChanges to this Privacy Policy are effective when they are posted on this\r\npage.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Contact Us</strong></h3>\r\nIf you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, You can contact us:\r\n\r\n· By email: ho@itums.co.in\r\n\r\n· By visiting this page on our website:\r\n<a href=\"https://itums.co.in/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\r\nhttps://itums.co.in/contact-us/\r\n</a>\r\n\r\n· By phone number: 033 4601 7088 / 033 4060 2084 / 98300 13731','Privacy Policy for ITU Management Services','At ITUMS, accessible from www.itums.co.in, one of our main priorities is the privacy of our visitors. This Privacy Policy document contains types of information that is collected and recorded by ITUMS and how we use it.','inherit','closed','closed','','716-revision-v1','','','2020-05-19 04:28:00','2020-05-19 04:28:00','',716,'https://itums.co.in/716-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(724,1,'2020-05-30 17:39:02','2020-05-30 17:39:02','[simple-sitemap]','Site map','','inherit','closed','closed','','723-revision-v1','','','2020-05-30 17:39:02','2020-05-30 17:39:02','',723,'https://itums.co.in/723-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(726,1,'2020-05-31 07:32:47','2020-05-31 07:32:47','','career','','inherit','open','closed','','career-3','','','2020-05-31 07:32:47','2020-05-31 07:32:47','',0,'https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/career-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(729,1,'2020-05-31 11:50:13','2020-05-31 11:50:13','','gallery','','inherit','open','closed','','gallery-2','','','2020-05-31 11:50:13','2020-05-31 11:50:13','',0,'https://itums.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/galle